# /etc/fw_env.config - intentionally empty for am3-bb.
#
# The am3-bb image reuses the shared am3 userspace overlay, but it must not
# inherit the Amlogic /dev/nand_env U-Boot environment layout. No AM335x
# fw_env layout is validated for this BeagleBone Black control-board path.
#
# Keep this file present with comments only so accidental fw_printenv/fw_setenv
# calls fail closed instead of writing an Amlogic NAND environment device.
